1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 15=

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,310
The plot is out of control.

22
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:26,950
If I still can't find a way out,

23
00:01:26,950 --> 00:01:28,000
I'll ruin everything!

24
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,840
Ye Jin.

25
00:01:31,310 --> 00:01:32,200
Your Highness.

26
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,510
What's wrong?

27
00:01:35,710 --> 00:01:37,790
You look awful.

28
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,840
I...

29
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,560
Consort Lan

30
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,920
just rewarded me
with many jewels and ornaments.

31
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:50,840
What did she ask you to do?

32
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,310
She wants me to drug Consort Duan

33
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,760
at the Empress Dowager's birthday feast.

34
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,600
Drug?

35
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:00,870
What kind of drug?

36
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:02,230
She said it's a laxative.

37
00:02:02,230 --> 00:02:03,870
Just to upset her stomach.

38
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:04,840
It won't kill her.

39
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,070
Consort Duan
is carrying an imperial heir now.

40
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,310
Harming the imperial heir

41
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:09,560
is a capital crime.

42
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,280
One wrong move.

43
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,430
Not only you and me,

44
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:14,360
but even my mother

45
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,400
can't escape blame.

46
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,870
Did you agree to her?

47
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:20,870
She... she threatened me.

48
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:23,430
She said she'd make me disappear,
so I...

49
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,430
Come here.

50
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,360
Leave this matter

51
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,590
to me.

52
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,750
Don't worry.

53
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:36,120
As long as I'm here,

54
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,680
I won't let you disappear.

55
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:40,270
Mm.

56
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:05,960
Grind this finer.

57
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,800
Okay.

58
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:10,840
Get some wolfberries.

59
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,240
The soup isn't colorful enough.

60
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:13,150
Just a little bit.

61
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:14,750
Yes.

62
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:31,360
May Your Majesty
live a long and healthy life.

63
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:33,520
All take your seats.

64
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:35,870
Thank you, Your Majesty.

65
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,800
Mother, I wish you

66
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:49,080
a long and blessed life.

67
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,750
Mother, you can try this later.

68
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:56,360
It's a tribute from Suzhou.

69
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,200
Mm.

70
00:03:57,520 --> 00:04:00,150
I wish Your Majesty
a thousand years

71
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,470
of blessings and peace.

72
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,520
Consort Lan, you are thoughtful.

73
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

74
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,950
Mother, I wish you

75
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:22,430
boundless blessings

76
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:23,800
and a long life.

77
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,950
Your legs aren't fully healed.

78
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:27,600
You must not drink any wine.

79
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,480
Brother,

80
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,120
rest well.

81
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,560
Mother.

82
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:39,030
I'm fine.

83
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,190
Your Majesty,

84
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,950
I offer tea instead of wine.

85
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:47,600
Wishing Your Majesty a joyful birthday

86
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,000
and a long life.

87
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,630
Take good care of your pregnancy.

88
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:51,750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

89
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:15,000
Please try this.

90
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,840
Your Majesty,

91
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,360
you try some too.

92
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:24,110
Your Ladyship.

93
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:25,350
It hurts.

94
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,560
Your Ladyship!

95
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,630
It hurts so much.

96
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,120
Consort Lan has a stomachache!

97
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:35,600
Hurry, summon the Imperial Physician!

98
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,670
Hurry.

99
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,310
Summon the Imperial Physician!

100
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,600
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager.

101
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,070
Consort Lan's stomachache

102
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,390
is caused by Qingteng Herb.

103
00:05:58,510 --> 00:06:00,360
It's not deadly poison.

104
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,920
But it causes sharp pain when heated.

105
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:05,120
If the dosage was higher,

106
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,190
the consequences would be severe.

107
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,720
What is this Qingteng Herb?

108
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:11,190
It's a rare herb
from the Western Regions.

109
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:12,360
Very rare.

110
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:16,070
How did it get into the palace feast?

111
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,600
Your Majesty.

112
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,750
Your Majesty.

113
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,560
Someone

114
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,040
tried to poison me.

115
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:29,920
You must uphold justice for me.

116
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,160
Your Majesty.

117
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,000
Guards,

118
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,190
take everyone from the kitchen

119
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:35,120
for interrogation!

120
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,920
And investigate all servers today.

121
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,840
Empress Dowager.

122
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:42,190
Your Majesty.

123
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:44,120
You must uphold justice for me.

124
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,600
What is happening now?

125
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,600
The poisoned soup

126
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:50,070
was not meant for Consort Lan.

127
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,630
It was for me.

128
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,510
Explain yourself.

129
00:06:55,730 --> 00:06:57,160
After Consort Lan got the stomachache,

130
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,630
I realized

131
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:01,240
the soup was poisoned.

132
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,560
So I sent people to
investigate the kitchen.

133
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:08,950
I never thought
my soup and Consort Lan's

134
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:10,270
would be swapped

135
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,720
halfway.

136
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,720
If that had not happened,

137
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,560
the one lying on the couch

138
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,830
would be me.

139
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,280
Guards.

140
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:22,000
Who served Consort Duan the soup today?

141
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:24,190
Bring her here.

142
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,310
Are you the one who served the soup?

143
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,640
Speak.

144
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,510
Why did you swap the bowls?

145
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:33,750
Your Majesty, spare me.

146
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,390
I swapped the bowls

147
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,600
because I didn't want to die.

148
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:46,040
It was Biqing from Consort Lan's palace.

149
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,800
She threatened my entire family's lives

150
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,190
to force me to
poison Consort Duan's soup.

151
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:53,070
I feared being implicated if it failed,

152
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:54,630
so I secretly switched it.

153
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,480
I'm innocent.

154
00:07:56,610 --> 00:07:57,870
I never threatened her.

155
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,270
Nor ordered her to poison anyone.

156
00:07:59,410 --> 00:08:00,280
Insolence!

157
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:03,000
Poisoning at the palace feast

158
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:05,480
can't be excused by innocence.

159
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:09,120
Take these two maids for interrogation.

160
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,860
Your Ladyship.

161
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,120
Your Ladyship, save me.

162
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,240
Your Ladyship!

163
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,720
Your Ladyship!

164
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,830
The evidence and witness are clear.

165
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:21,000
Biqing is from your palace.

166
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,240
How do you explain this?

167
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,000
Your Majesty.

168
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,510
I...

169
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,920
I was framed.

170
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,630
Consort Lan poisoned a fellow consort.

171
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:32,000
This is a grave offense!

172
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,840
Sixi.

173
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,960
Deliver my order.

174
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,750
Consort Lan failed to
control her people.

175
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,240
Strip her title immediately.

176
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,120
Your Majesty.

177
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,240
Demote her to Consort.

178
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:40,840
Revoke her palace authority.

179
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,320
Yes, Your Majesty.

180
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,360
Your Majesty!

181
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:46,510
Your Majesty.

182
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,840
Your Majesty.

183
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,320
I was wronged.

184
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:51,960
My birthday feast

185
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:54,480
has been ruined by you.

186
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:58,440
The harem needs to be disciplined.

187
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,320
Your Majesty.

188
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:02,270
Your Majesty.

189
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,910
You lowly maid.

190
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:13,790
How dare you betray me?

191
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:16,440
She begged Biqing tearfully

192
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,840
to save her family..

193
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:20,200
Now she dares to
bite the hand that fed her.

194
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,870
This is utter outrage!

195
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,630
Calm down, Your Ladyship.

196
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,630
This involves too many people.

197
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:27,750
One wrong move

198
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,950
will cause chaos in the palace.

199
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,390
I think

200
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:32,510
His Majesty only
demoted Your Ladyship to Consort

201
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:33,840
and didn't press further.

202
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,550
That's already in honor of old ties.

203
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:37,390
In honor of old ties?

204
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,720
If he truly cared,

205
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,910
how could he humiliate me

206
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:45,080
in front of everyone?

207
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,910
Your Ladyship,
you're still a Consort.

208
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:50,200
If you stay calm,

209
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,030
you'll rise again soon.

210
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:58,390
Rise again?

211
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:02,120
I must first endure this humiliation.

212
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,750
Biqing is loyal.

213
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:08,600
She took all the blame.

214
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:11,320
But she knows all my secrets.

215
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,550
Keeping her in the Punishment Office

216
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:16,240
will bring trouble

217
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:19,320
and more problems.

218
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,320
I understand.

219
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,360
I'll make her

220
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,790
leave properly and with dignity.

221
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:32,200
Your Majesty, you've worked hard today.

222
00:10:32,390 --> 00:10:34,550
The scenery is nice here.

223
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:37,840
Why not rest in the pavilion?

224
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,720
The scenery is nice.

225
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,360
Watching dance here

226
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:42,910
must be special.

227
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:46,360
Your Majesty,
have you forgotten Lady Xiao...

228
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:53,150
Your Majesty, shall we summon the
dancers from the Southern Music Bureau?

229
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:06,870
Your Majesty.

230
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,960
I didn't arrange this.

231
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:11,910
This dancer does not seem to be from
the Southern Music Bureau.

232
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,910
Though her dancing is a bit clumsy,

233
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,960
she's lively.

234
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,750
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

235
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,550
You served the Emperor last night.

236
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,630
How was it?

237
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:27,360
I got you out of the Cold Palace

238
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,030
and brought you to His Majesty.

239
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:32,000
Now you're a Second Attendant.

240
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:34,200
You've risen high.

241
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:36,440
I will never forget

242
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,440
the Your Ladyship's kindness
in lifting me up.

243
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:40,030
Rise.

244
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,360
Since you got what you wanted,

245
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:45,270
then serve me well from this day on.

246
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:47,360
I will not treat you unfairly.

247
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,030
Yes.

248
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,840
Whitening Pill.

249
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,720
Take a fixed dose every day.

250
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,240
It will keep your skin fair

251
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,720
and glowing.

252
00:13:05,030 --> 00:13:08,200
If it didn't stop pregnancy,

253
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:10,440
I'd take them too.

254
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,200
Attendant Xi,

255
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:19,200
sacrificing fertility for favor.

256
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,630
You don't hate me, right?

257
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:32,600
This was my own choice.

258
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:36,630
Your Ladyship, you've been favored
since entering the palace.

259
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:38,840
You never felt

260
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:41,120
the pain of being ignored.

261
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,150
If I can't even gain favor

262
00:13:44,910 --> 00:13:46,030
or

263
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:48,440
can't even see His Majesty,

264
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,910
then even if I can have children,

265
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,480
what's the point?

266
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:55,600
You do have some nerve.

267
00:13:56,790 --> 00:13:59,000
Then make full use of your talents.

268
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,550
I

269
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:03,390
shall await your good news.

270
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:08,870
Farewell, Your Ladyship.

271
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,290
What?

272
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:25,030
Catch up, old friends?

273
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,120
Between you and me,

274
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,510
what past is there to talk about?

275
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,030
Is that so?

276
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,790
Insolence.

277
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:38,390
How dare you damage the fan
bestowed by His Majesty?

278
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:40,030
Kneel and apologize now.

279
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:42,840
Maybe I'll spare you.

280
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,700
You...

281
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:45,600
You broke it yourself.

282
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,480
You all saw it.

283
00:14:47,910 --> 00:14:50,440
Who broke the fan just now?

284
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,630
Naturally, it was Lady Xiao.

285
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:56,750
Liumei.

286
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,670
My face is ruined now.

287
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,720
I can no longer
compete for favor with you.

288
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:02,790
Why are you still picking on me?

289
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:12,200
I, Qijia Liumei,

290
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,870
am from the Eight Banners.

291
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:15,630
I am a noble by birth.

292
00:15:15,630 --> 00:15:16,550
And you?

293
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:20,320
Just a commoner from the Han Banner.

294
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:22,390
How dare you compare with me?

295
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,960
Relying on your looks

296
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,720
to seduce and win favor.

297
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,550
In the end, it is only

298
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,440
a fleeting illusion.

299
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,910
And now...

300
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,550
You face is ruined.

301
00:15:33,550 --> 00:15:35,270
You even have no way out.

302
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:37,080
So pathetic

303
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:39,390
and ridiculous.

304
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:45,120
Aren't you just jealous
that she's better looking?

305
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,080
Attendant Liu.

306
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:50,030
You're so malicious.

307
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:52,030
Who is this lowly maid?

308
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:54,630
How dare you talk back?

309
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:55,870
Guards,

310
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,150
slap her.

311
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:59,750
I am a sixth-rank official physician
of Cining Palace.

312
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:01,440
If you want to slap me,

313
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,790
it is not your place.

314
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:06,240
My Lady, she's the one the Empress Dowager
gave to the 14th Prince.

315
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,550
She's just a common maid.

316
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,840
She is not fit even to
carry 14th Prince's shoes.

317
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,240
No title,

318
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:14,200
still riding on others' power.

319
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:16,510
Today, I will beat you myself.

320
00:16:16,630 --> 00:16:17,840
Who can stop me?

321
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,160
Hit her!

322
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,160
Stop.

323
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:27,200
Ye Jin is my Secondary Consort.

324
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,790
Even if she's wrong,

325
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,550
it is not your place to discipline her.

326
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:32,320
Y... Your Majesty.

327
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:34,630
I was just joking.

328
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:35,630
Sixi.

329
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:36,910
Yes.

330
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:39,030
Lady Qijia misbehaved

331
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:40,000
and has no virtue.

332
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,390
Demote her to Second Attendant.

333
00:16:41,390 --> 00:16:42,630
Move her out of Xianfu Palace

334
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:44,240
to the Buddhist hall
in Lengxiang Garden.

335
00:16:44,260 --> 00:16:45,200
Stay in and reflect there.

336
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,510
Yes, Your Majesty.

337
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,320
Secondary Consort?

338
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,000
This is my wish.

339
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,320
I haven't told mother yet.

340
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:03,550
You're such a romantic.

341
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,590
Rejecting a noble lady

342
00:17:06,350 --> 00:17:08,200
for a lowly maid.

343
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:10,510
Do you know

344
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,920
why mother insists you marry

345
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:13,400
Tongjia Baozhu?

346
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,920
I

347
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:17,160
naturally understand.

348
00:17:17,590 --> 00:17:20,510
But I think she worries too much.

349
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:26,720
Mother's love for you

350
00:17:27,110 --> 00:17:28,240
has all been given to you.

351
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:29,400
Sometimes

352
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,880
I'm really jealous.

353
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,240
Fine.

354
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:36,030
Since you love this maid,

355
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,790
then as your elder brother,

356
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,590
granting your wish is no hard matter.

357
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,240
But you must understand,

358
00:17:41,550 --> 00:17:42,400
if you truly take

359
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,550
this maid as your Secondary Consort,

360
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,920
that General of Martial Might

361
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,920
may not be willing to
marry his daughter to you.

362
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,750
Losing a powerful in-law family.

363
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,880
Don't regret it later.

364
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,510
Thank you for your approval,
Your Majesty.

365
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,350
This is my true wish.

366
00:17:57,550 --> 00:17:58,590
I'll never regret.

367
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,310
Since you both agree,

368
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,480
I'll grant your wish.

369
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:04,680
Maid Ye Jin

370
00:18:08,530 --> 00:18:11,000
is granted marriage to the 14th Prince
and titled Secondary Consort.

371
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:12,550
Choose an auspicious date
for the wedding.

372
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:14,920
Thank you, Your Majesty.

373
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:17,790
Farewell, Your Majesty.

374
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,960
What mutual agreement?

375
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:26,200
I never agreed.

376
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,040
This...

377
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:30,000
Wasn't this just a temporary measure?

378
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,720
A temporary measure?

379
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:33,590
His Majesty has ordered the marriage.

380
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,110
What, gonna back out now?

381
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:38,480
If you really refuse,

382
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:42,110
I'll find a way later.

383
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,270
But the situation isn't stable.

384
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:46,030
Under my protection

385
00:18:46,030 --> 00:18:48,160
is better than you being alone
in this harem

386
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,200
at someone else's mercy.

387
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:50,510
Right?

388
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:03,080
♪I am but an outsider♪

389
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:05,280
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

390
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:09,560
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

391
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:13,800
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

392
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:21,320
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

393
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:24,880
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

394
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:27,400
♪I know how this story ends♪

395
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:31,960
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

396
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:36,400
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

397
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:44,680
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

398
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:47,960
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

399
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:51,240
♪A history that no one can search♪

400
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:54,760
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

401
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:56,560
♪I am but an outsider♪

402
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:58,800
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

403
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:02,840
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

404
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:07,520
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

405
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:14,840
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

406
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:18,200
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

407
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:20,680
♪I know how this story ends♪

408
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:24,840
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

409
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:28,120
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

410
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:31,920
♪Please forget me and move on♪

411
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:38,160
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

412
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:49,680
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

413
00:20:53,240 --> 00:21:02,960
♪When do I finally wake♪
